TASKS 2.1:IDENTIFICATION OF PROJECT REQUIREMENTS

📌 Project Scope
Objective: Develop a mobile app that delivers real-time updates on sustainability initiatives and provides personalized carbon footprint reduction tips.

Target Audience: Environmentally-conscious customers and stakeholders of Green Tech Solutions.

Boundaries: Focus on customer engagement and awareness — not internal operations or unrelated services.

Deliverables:

Mobile application (iOS & Android)

Admin dashboard for content management

Analytics and reporting tools for engagement tracking

📝 Project Requirements
1. Functional Requirements
Real-Time Updates

Push notifications for new sustainability initiatives, events, and campaigns.

Personalized Tips

Tailored recommendations based on user profile (location, lifestyle, preferences).

Carbon Footprint Tracker

Simple calculator to estimate and monitor individual impact.

Gamification

Badges, challenges, and rewards for eco-friendly actions.

Community Engagement

Forums or discussion boards for sharing ideas and success stories.

Integration

Link with social media for sharing achievements.

Sync with external sustainability data sources (e.g., local recycling programs).

2. Non-Functional Requirements
Usability

Intuitive interface, accessible design, multilingual support.

Performance

Fast loading times, reliable push notifications.

Scalability

Ability to handle growing user base and expanding features.

Security

Data privacy compliance (GDPR, local laws).

Compatibility

Cross-platform (iOS, Android), responsive design for different devices.

3. Stakeholder Needs
Customers

Easy access to sustainability updates.

Personalized, actionable eco-tips.

Recognition for their contributions.

Management

Increased customer engagement metrics.

Insights into user behavior and preferences.

Marketing Team

Ability to push targeted campaigns.

Analytics on customer participation.

IT Team

Secure, maintainable, and scalable system.














